The paper deals with privacy-preserving cloud storage, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The focus is on synchronization and backup services, which are related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the proposed solution, which is related to database systems (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE).
